# sdkconfig.defaults.rev6
#
# Rev 6 specific overrides. Most settings come from sdkconfig.defaults.
#
# Currently empty — Rev 6 and Rev 7 use the same ESP32-S3-WROOM-1-N16R8
# module and the same flash layout. This file exists as a placeholder for
# future rev-specific config (e.g. clock tuning, peripheral enables).
